item.description:
We bring your dreams to life. Industrial Design & Design Engineering is our core strength and we also specialize in Communication Design.You have a product idea in your mind ? Great! We can help you bring it to life.You want to get your product ready for manufacturing ? Super, you’re already pass half the design battle so let’s get you ready with all the engineering support you need.You have your product ready to ship but need help with packaging & other communication solutions ? Don’t worry, our super awesome team can get you the design language you need to get your product the visibility it deserves.

Hannan Hakim Designs is a multi disciplinary design studio based in Pune, India.
